Title: Tending to the Terrified
Description:
All happen so fast. One moment, we gathering eggs and grubs. Next, spiders swarming.

Nebb drag me here,  many others trapped. Caught in webs, soon to be feasts. Must save the Grubtenders. 

We tenders, not fighters. Do not let friends become meals.
CompletionText: Hurry. Spiders prefer grubs, but spiders very hungry.
RewardText: Aha, Grubtenders free! They survive to harvest again.
